The drummer & lead vocals in this set of "Four Seasons" is Gary Polci. He's the music teacher at our High School in NJ. All 3 of my children were in his classes. About 10 yrs ago, he was holding our yearly Talent Night & 1 of the acts had dropped out. I'm sitting in the audience, curtains were closed... slowly they opened & there's Gary on stage alone sitting at his drum set & starts to bang out that old familiar tune. Every ADULT in the audience (especially the women) jumped up screaming. haha!! He sang the whole song. A night I'll NEVER, EVER forget!!!
